  "time_ut": 1661680268,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db4\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dca \u0d91\u0d9a\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0d86 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0d86\u0db4\u0dc3\u0dd4 \u0dba\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A foreigner who came to this country with a passport is sent back",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Katunayake Airport Immigration Department officials took steps to deport a Bangladeshi national who tried to enter the country with a Sri Lankan passport on the same flight he came from.",
        "He had arrived at Katunayake airport by Al Jazeera flight from Kuwait.",
        "After that, he came to the airport immigration counter to get the necessary clearances to enter the country and presented the Sri Lankan passport along with other necessary documents to the immigration officer who was on duty there.",
        "The officer of the Immigration Department who observed the passport, had managed to uncover the facts that it belonged to a Sri Lankan and was later misplaced.",
        "The officials of that department had succeeded in discovering that the photo in the passport was fake, and during the initial investigations.",
        "After that, this person has been referred to the Katunayake Airport Chief Immigration Department Officer for further investigation.",
        "There, steps were taken to check his wallet and suitcase, where it was possible to find an identification certificate issued by the Bangladesh Embassy in the State of Kuwait.",
        "It has also been revealed that this Bangladeshi national has prepared a Sri Lankan passport to come to this country through a broker in Kuwait."
      ],
